DESCRIPTION

    EARLY RELEASE, MORE EXAMPLES TO COME, CONTRIBUTIONS WELCOME.

    This distribution, as the name suggests, contains a collection of
    various examples of Perl modules/scripts. If you happen to need a
    script/module that:

      * contains some warnings and errors

      * downloads some stuffs from the Internet using {LWP,HTTP::Tiny,...}

      * contains an endless loop

      * creates a circular data structure

      * generates some random text

      * do some busy work for X seconds/minutes

      * demonstrates some Perl features

      * and so on

    but don't want to have to write it yourself, then this distribution is
    for you.

